Little's Baby Powder Puff (Pink)

Little?s Powder Puff is specially designed for your baby. The puff contains a special chamber for filling baby powder that can be accessed by unscrewing its handle. This is to ensure that the baby powder is spread uniformly on your baby?s skin. The jar of the powder puff has a screw-on lid to prevent accidental spillages of powder.
